<l>kamiva nāma na bāhulatāntatraṃ priyatamāyatamānayadīpsitam||60||</l>
</lg>
<p xml:id="HV_03_60p">[iti varṣāḥ]</p>
<lg type="verse" xml:id="HV_03_61">
<l>sphuritacārutarāpaghanaśriyā hṛdayanandanaśobhanaveṣayā|</l>
